    <p>That is where a machinery equipment loan comes in. At Ing Heng Credit, we understand that for many SMEs, cash flow is king. We have helped thousands of businesses across Malaysia get the tools they need without the stress of bank-style bureaucracy. Let’s look at how you can use a machinery loan to grow your business while keeping your cash in the bank.</p>

